{
  "page": "Battle for the Dawn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with the <a href=\"/index.php/War_for_the_dawn\" title=\"War for the dawn\">war for the dawn</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle for the Dawn</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"T Jedruszek songofnight.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/57/T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg/350px-T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/57/T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg/525px-T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/57/T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg/700px-T_Jedruszek_songofnight.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><div style=\"width:100%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">Wights</a> attack the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>.<br />Art by Tomasz Jedruszek</div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/The_Long_Night\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Long Night\">The Long Night</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nDefeat of the <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a><br />End of the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a> and the endless winter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/45px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/60px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">the Others</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p>The <b>Battle for the Dawn</b> was a legendary battle against the <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> which marked the end of the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is possibly connected with the legends of <a href=\"/index.php/Azor_Ahai\" title=\"Azor Ahai\">Azor Ahai</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/The_prince_that_was_promised\" title=\"The prince that was promised\">the prince that was promised</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_hero\" title=\"Last hero\">last hero</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_for_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the midst of the darkness of the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> emerged from the <a href=\"/index.php/Lands_of_Always_Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lands of Always Winter\">far north</a>, wielding razor-thin swords of ice and raising <a href=\"/index.php/Wight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wight\">the dead</a> to fight the living. The <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> and their allies, the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>, fought against them, but were driven southwards by their advance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The Others were eventually checked when it was discovered that weapons made of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonglass\" title=\"Dragonglass\">dragonglass</a> could kill them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to the song \"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Night_That_Ended\" title=\"The Night That Ended\">The Night That Ended</a>\", the first members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> rode against the Others and drove them back north in the Battle for the Dawn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">Maesters</a> generally believe the defeat of the Others and the construction of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> occurred six thousand years ago, although <i><a href=\"/index.php/True_History\" title=\"True History\">True History</a></i> states these events were eight thousand years ago.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_for_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(game)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (game)\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i> RPG and Resource Book</a>, Guardians of Order</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, Bran IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_21\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 21\">Chapter 21</a>, Bran III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Long Night.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404135554\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.054 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.207 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 491/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9299/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7509/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 653/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2280/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  195.108      1 -total\n 80.98%  157.995   